      "text": "Roadmap for a project from beginning to completion\n\n\n1.Read The project requirement or requirement analysis throughly\n2.brainstorming\n3.note down improtant topics emp: entities, features ,roles , api endpoints\n4.note down the flow of the project :user role(role based)\n5.erd design\n6.project setup with required tech stack\n7.prisma schema models defining\n8.prisma migrate and genarate\n9.project business logic implementation\n10.check  new feature and test the completed features",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
