      "text": "Prisma Overview\n\n1.project planning to completion\n2.brainstorm,Requirment Analysis,ER Design\n3.Project Set up +Prisma Connected\n4.Prisma Schema And Model\n5.Multi file prisma schema\n6.Prisma Migration,CLient Generation\n7.Server And App Set Up.app test by Demo api\n8. User Register Router :api/users/register\n9.Moduler Pattern \n10.Server Handle Core business logic and database communicationa and queries\n11.controller handles and catches the errors\n12.try catch block inside controller\n13.Password hashing\n\n",
